PersonalMission.Name: SPG-15: War Gods
PersonalMission.Description: An SPG that survives for as long as possible is a real asset for the team. Keep firing one shell after another while trying not to get caught under enemy fire. Take your time and think twice before \"pulling the trigger\", since \"one shot—one hit\" is the best strategy for a vehicle with a long reload time.

Primary.Conditions:
•  Be among the top 3 players on your team by experience earned
•  Enable your allies to cause 1,500 HP of damage to enemy vehicles by stunning or immobilizing them
